<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̉nạ bạldm fạdyky</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉nạ bạldm fạdyky .. dmy sfkth lyky
 wbdmy mgẖṭyky .. gẖạlyẗ yạ ạ̉rḍy ʿlyã)2
 1- (ạ̹nty yạ ạ̉rḍy gẖạlyẗ ʿlyã .. ạ̹ʿlạn ḥby jrwḥ fy ạ̹ydyã
 dmy whbth lyky ʿṭyẗ .. byḥqq kl wʿwdy lyky)2
 2- (dạ bạsmk nrfʿ ạ̉yạdynạ .. nʿln dmk rạyẗ ʿlynạ
 kl blạdnạ tʿly fạdynạ .. dạ ạ̹lhnạ mtmsk byky)2
 3- (ḥqq kl wʿwdk lynạ .. tyjy wtskn fy wsṭynạ
 wtbạrk ạ̹nt ạ̉rạḍynạ .. ạlly btndh lk yạ mlyky)2</lyrics>
<hymn_number>366</hymn_number>
<author>hrmạs smyr, hrmạs smyr</author>
</song>